# Factor Out Views and API Modules

- Keep page-level views under `frontend/src/views/`.
- Keep `App.tsx` focused on shell composition and routing, not feature-specific view logic.
- Keep API modules under `frontend/src/api/` with one domain file per entity area and shared infra in `core.ts`.
